{"expireTime":9007200809748944000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-html-a7d04d378a70bda423eac424ff6d5553-gatsby-remark-imagesgatsby-remark-responsive-iframegatsby-remark-prismjsgatsby-remark-copy-linked-filesgatsby-remark-autolink-headers-","val":"<h1 id=\"pointlight\"><a href=\"#pointlight\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PointLight</h1>\n<p>Create a point light source which emits from a point in all directions.Point lights attenuation is not available. At most 5 directional lights can be supported.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<p>Create a point light source with color, intensity and position.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> pointLight<span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PointLight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  color<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">128</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">128</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  intensity<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2.0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  position<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"methods\"><a href=\"#methods\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Methods</h2>\n<h3 id=\"constructor\"><a href=\"#constructor\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>constructor</h3>\n<p>The constructor for the <code class=\"language-text\">PointLight</code> class. Use this to create a new <code class=\"language-text\">PointLight</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> pointLight <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PointLight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>color<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> intensity<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> position<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"parameters\"><a href=\"#parameters\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Parameters</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">color</code> - (<em>array</em>,)  RGB color of point light source, default value is <code class=\"language-text\">[255, 255, 255]</code>.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">intensity</code> - (<em>number</em>) Strength of point light source, default value is <code class=\"language-text\">1.0</code>.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">position</code> - (<em>array</em>,)  Location of point light source, default value is <code class=\"language-text\">[0, 0, 1]</code>.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">attenuation</code> - (<em>array</em>,)  Attenuation of point light source based on distance.\nIn order of Constant, Linear, Exponential components.\nFor details see <a href=\"http://ogldev.atspace.co.uk/www/tutorial20/tutorial20.html\">this tutorial</a>.\nUse <code class=\"language-text\">[1, 0, 0]</code> for no attenuation. Default value is <code class=\"language-text\">[0, 0, 1]</code>.</li>\n</ul>"}